#Weather Forecast App

A modern and responsive Weather Forecast Application developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project fetches real-time weather data from a weather API and presents it through a clean, interactive, and user-friendly interface.

The application allows users to view current weather conditions, temperature, humidity, wind information, and forecast details in a visually appealing dashboard.

## 🚀 Features

* Real-Time Weather Updates
* Current Temperature Display
* Weather Condition Information
* Humidity and Wind Speed Details
* Multi-Day Weather Forecast
* Dynamic Weather Icons
* Responsive Design for Mobile and Desktop
* Smooth UI Animations
* Clean and Modern User Interface

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (ES6)
* Weather API
* Font Awesome
* Google Fonts

## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates how external APIs can be integrated into frontend applications to display live data. The application retrieves weather information from a weather service and dynamically updates the interface based on the received data.

The primary goal of this project was to improve frontend development skills while gaining hands-on experience with API integration, asynchronous JavaScript, and responsive web design.

## 🎯 Learning Outcomes

Through this project, I gained practical experience in:

* API Integration
* Fetching and Processing JSON Data
* JavaScript DOM Manipulation
* Responsive Web Design
* CSS Layouts and Animations
* Error Handling in API Requests
* Building Interactive User Interfaces

## 📷 Application Sections

* Current Weather Information
* Weather Status Display
* Temperature Overview
* Humidity & Wind Details
* Forecast Cards
* Responsive Navigation

